==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blob
<hw>Blob</hw> <pr>(bl⟦ocr⟧b)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Bleb</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Something blunt and round; a
small drop or lump of something viscid or thick; a drop; a bubble; a
blister.</def> <rj><au>Wright.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small fresh-water fish
(<spn>Uranidea Richardsoni</spn>); the miller's thumb.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blobber</ent>⟦br⟧
